					</div>
				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: Running Out of Marijuana</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-01-06T18:05:16+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">January 6, 2014 1:05 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">January 6, 2014 1:05 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Washington</b></p>
<ul>
<li>As Congress heads <a href="//news.yahoo.com/obama-eyes-modest-momentum-capitol-hill-2014-134451018--finance.html">into the new year</a>, debates on unemployment insurance, budget spending and the government&#8217;s borrowing limit are expected to occur in quick succession.</li>
<li>The White House offers a <a href="//presspass.nbcnews.com/_news/2014/01/05/22188348-white-house-offers-grand-bargain-on-tax-cuts-and-infrastructure?lite">grand bargain</a> on tax cuts and infrastructure.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<ul>
<li>The Associated Press takes a look into <a href="//www.tulsaworld.com/business/smallbusiness/small-business-looking-into-crystal-ball-for/article_c2436f0e-1104-56e6-9d9e-ca807f93134d.html">a crystal ball</a> for small businesses.</li>
<li>Recent <a href="//www.ritholtz.com/blog/2014/01/better-than-expected-us-economic-data/">data</a> show a strengthening economy.</li>
<li>Here are 10 things <a href="//money.cnn.com/gallery/pf/2014/01/05/pay-more-2014/">youâll pay more</a> for in 2014.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span id="more-81564"></span><br />
<b>People</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Minimum wages are <a href="//business.time.com/2013/12/30/minimum-wage-to-rise-in-13-states-in-2014/">set to rise</a> in 13 states this year, and a new report finds that increasing the minimum wage may <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2014/01/04/economists-agree-raising-the-minimum-wage-reduces-poverty/?">help fight</a> poverty. But <a href="//www.zerohedge.com/news/2014-01-05/guest-post-minimum-wage-forces-low-skill-workers-compete-higher-skill-workers">others worry that</a> it could reduce employment among low-skilled workers.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Finance</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Sherwood Neiss <a href="//venturebeat.com/2014/01/02/it-might-cost-you-39k-to-crowdfund-100k-under-the-secs-new-rules/">warns</a> that it may cost $39,000 to finance $100,000 under the Security and Exchange Commissionâs proposed crowdfunding rules.</li>
<li>Bitcoin <a href="//www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-01-05/bitcoin-tops-1-000-again-on-adoption-by-zynga-amid-wider-usage.html">tops $1,000</a> again.</li>
<li>PayPal extends its <a href="//finovate.com/2014/01/paypal-extends-working-capital-pilot-program-to-support-small-business-lending.html">working capital pilot program</a> to support small-business lending.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Management</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Annie Sisk says the <a href="//pajamaproductivity.com/the-only-resolution-you-need-this-year/">only resolution</a> you need to make this year is to âcreate an in-your-face method and system of tracking your progress and reminding yourself constantly of your goals and intentions.â</li>
<li>This is how <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/article/230303">three franchise owners</a> beat the odds â and how a science teacher <a href="//www.buzzfeed.com/rachelzarrell/a-science-teacher-lost-37-pounds-from-an-experiment-where-he">lost 37 pounds</a> eating only at McDonald&#8217;s.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Sales</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Here are a few tips for avoiding a <a href="//www.theworkathomewoman.com/post-holiday-sales-slump/">post-holiday sales</a> slump.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Social Media</b></p>
<ul>
<li>If youâre a dentist, here are a few <a href="//rabidofficemonkey.com/2014/01/social-media-networks-dental-practice-active/?">social media networks</a> that you should be active on.</li>
<li>This is one benefit of <a href="//blogs.constantcontact.com/product-blogs/social-media-marketing/benefits-facebook-business-page/">having a Facebook page</a> that most business owners overlook.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Around the Country</b></p>
<ul>
<li>A Sacramento company <a href="//on.aol.com/video/company-gives-12-people-the-gift-of-hearing-518071884?">gives 12 people</a> the gift of hearing.</li>
<li>Manhattan <a href="//www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/01/03/manhattan-apartment-sales_n_4537156.html">apartment sales</a> are at a 25-year high.</li>
<li>An infographic from a trucking company shows 2013&#8217;s <a href="//www.atlasvanlines.com/infographics/2013-migration-patterns/">migration patterns</a>.</li>
<li>Recreational marijuana is legalized in Colorado and <a href="//www.policymic.com/articles/78143/marijuana-sales-in-colorado-top-1-million-on-first-day">first day sales</a> top $1 million. But Colorado marijuana shops are expected to <a href="//www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/01/05/bummer-colorado-pot-shops-will-run-out-of-marijuana-within-days/">run out</a> of marijuana within days. Executives at High Times, a publication that has covered the marijuana scene for four decades, are introducing a new <a href="//www.denverpost.com/business/ci_24844193/high-times-launches-fund-cannabis-investment">private-equity fund</a> that is expected to boost Colorado&#8217;s newest industry.</li>
<li>States that vote Republican have <a href="//www.aei-ideas.org/2014/01/states-that-vote-republican-have-higher-volunteer-rates-than-states-leaning-left/">higher volunteer rates</a> than states that lean left.</li>
<li>A Boston bar serves up <a href="//www.today.com/video/today/53986033#53986033">a different kind</a> of âgirls&#8217; night out.â</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Taxes</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Donât <a href="//www.forbes.com/sites/tomtaulli/2014/01/05/need-to-worry-about-sending-out-1099-misc-forms/">forget to file</a> your 1099-MISC forms this month.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Technology</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Yahoo <a href="//www.usatoday.com/story/money/business/2014/01/05/yahoo-servers-malware-attack/4327041/">gets hit</a> with a malware attack.</li>
<li>These <a href="//www.forbes.com/sites/louiscolumbus/2014/01/04/best-and-worst-performing-cloud-computing-stocks-of-2013/">cloud computing companies</a> had the best performing stocks of 2013.</li>
<li>More than <a href="//www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-ces-internet-things-20140105,0,3796601.story#axzz2pZimWsjQ">150,000 people</a> are expected to descend on Las Vegas for the Consumer Electronics Show.</li>
<li>Foxconn, the Taiwanese tech giant, is <a href="//www.nbcphiladelphia.com/news/local/Foxconn-Set-to-Scout-Pa-Sites-for-30-Million-Plant-238771421.html">scouting Pennsylvania locations</a> to build a $30 million plant.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><em>Gene Marks owns the Marks Group, a Bala Cynwyd, Pa., a consulting firm that helps clients with customer relationship management. You can follow him on <a href="https://www.twitter.com/genemarks">Twitter</a>.</em></p>
